name: Momosuzu Nene (Hololive) all outfits
description:
🐻 Kon-nene! Features 4 official outfits: nene_official (Orange dress, normal + bear), nene_original (China dress), nene_casual (brown sweater, twintails + side ponytail), and nene_kimono (New Years 2022); as well as a general "momosuzu nene" tag for all your other needs.

For a prompt comparison check the second example image.

Observations:

  • The casual outfit is missing the variation without the brown sweater, and the variation with the green coat, as there were almost no examples to train with.

  • No official bikini, but can do normal bikinis just fine.

  • The "momosuzu nene" tag might force a collar without prompting it, to fix this simply include the "collarbone" tag.

Works at weight 1.

Made using my Lora guide and Derrian's image sorter.
